  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard cabane rooms </strong>sleep 2-3 people and are <span>18 m</span><sup>2</sup>. These rooms have one double bed and one optional bunk bed which is imbedded into the wall. These rooms have a shower room with WC.</p>
<p><strong>Family/friends cabane rooms </strong>sleep 2-4 people and are <span>22 m</span><sup>2</sup>. These rooms have one double bed and 2 single loft beds suitable for adults. These rooms have a shower room with WC.</p>
<p><strong>Grand cabane rooms </strong>sleep 2-6 people are are <span>39 m</span><sup>2</sup>. These rooms have one large double bed, three single beds and one loft bed suitable for under 12s. These rooms have a bathroom with a bathtub, shower head and WC. </p>
<p><strong>Room facilites:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Desk</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Wake-up service </li>
<li>Towels </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
